= How to write a CM book

This section explains how to create a CM book and its content, following these steps:
* Install the {:required software|cmb_software}.
* Make a {:local copy of a book|cmb_local}.
* {:cmb_configure} the book.
* Create a {:hierarchy of folders and pages|cmb_pages} and the corresponding table of content.
* Write and format text using various {:cm} features.

